      "review_summary": "The branch adds transient reply target state to the Control UI chat, a right-click reply context menu, a reply preview bar, quoted-Markdown send handling, CSS, and chat view tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +347, Tests +121. Total +468 across 9 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the PR defect: source inspection and CI both show the latest head calls a removed renderWorkspaceFileRail path in renderChat. As a user-facing feature request, current-main reproduction is source-level absence rather than a broken existing contract.",
